Conclusion:
In the nutshell, the project will help all the cricket lovers to be in touch and even help them making new friends in the same game. This will let people know who are available at what time to play. Furthermore, this will also allow people to fix their schedules for the game. People will enjoy different levels of the game, as the level goes up the competition will go up as well. People will also be able to play the matches and get the result for the same. This project allows the people to get the scoring for the top team and will also help teams to improve their performance as they will be getting the tips to improve themselves.
